# Blog Content Collection

Add markdown blog posts here with frontmatter matching the schema in content/config.ts.

Example frontmatter:
---
title: "Your Blog Title"
description: "A brief description of the blog post"
publishDate: 2026-04-15
author: "Author Name"
category: "tutorials" # tutorials, reviews, news, guides
tags: ["v0", "tutorial"]
featured: false
---

Your markdown content here...
